  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Start of Your Main Phase] You may play 1 [Veemon] or [Wormmon]
    from your hand without paying the cost. At the next end of your opponent\u2019s
    turn, return it to the hand. [Your Turn] When one of your Digimon digivolves
    into a blue or green Digimon, by suspending this Tamer, gain 1 memory. If DNA
    digivolving, trash any 3 digivolution cards under your opponent's Digimon."
